{"tid":1527881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對於今日機場嘅實際情況我真係有少少野想講","createTime":"2019-09-01T11:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T13:59:56.000Z","uid":194069,"like":118,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"524c7ddf0eb1b2f9fedcbe25fcf36f766171d053","tid":1527881,"uid":194069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:46:56.000Z","msg":"大家搞清楚今日入黎嘅意義係咩啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">癱瘓交通呀屌你 </span></strong></span><br />\n癱瘓到一陣 航班有冇取消呀？<br />\n冇呀<br />\n難得號召到咁多人 全撚部人走曬<br />\n咪通返車囉 咁仲有咩意義啊？<br />\n一早就話咩冇gear和理非要走<br />\n點解冇gear就要走？<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當時仲有好多遊客行路入緊黎㗎</span></span><br />\n人地都未撚驚啦<br />\n<br />\n仲有一開始防暴啱啱到分左兩邊人散 <br />\n有大批手足比人逼左去機場個邊比人包抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己退左去大公路個邊 係唯一嘅出路<br />\n我屌你老母 呢個時候有好多散水撚出黎話咩要撤啦和理非 冇車點點點<br />\n我屌 咁入面個班手足點算呀？<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又大難臨頭各自飛</span></span>。<br />\n真係好嬲架個個moment<br />\n要散 可以散開d 但唔撚係撤囉 起碼你都要等佢地出翻黎一齊行set下rb咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後真係決定左撤 <br />\n一走就成班人走 佢要推 你人多嘅話一定可以慢慢同佢磨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比時間我地手足慢慢走<br />\n但係呢？一早就有散水撚叫走 全部人一齊出去即係封鐵<br />\n結果咪好似依家咁大圍困囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n滿意啦開心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問撚左好多次點解要走 點解唔可以用人數同佢慢慢磨慢慢推 加上一路都有遊客<br />\n但比人話要尊重前線<br />\n唉啱，今次做得唔好 要檢討<br />\n冇鐵有咩對策<br />\n點都唔會割 和勇一家親"},{"pid":"68ed880e89ede74483ad2fdb4040bd180ae9fb72","tid":1527881,"uid":194069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:47:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe8b006baad4f043312ccc039a04ad5664df5d10","tid":1527881,"uid":194069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:47:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6d023d4ad12d4af8d207fbd8c06d68be2c05326","tid":1527881,"uid":194069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:48:10.000Z","msg":"92.3 三罷"},{"pid":"d03a9af5352e4d8cfd374b5567ed71049d1ba555","tid":1527881,"uid":194069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:48:20.000Z","msg":"92.3 三罷"},{"pid":"0d1ad41e2511a9179f106dab46b1312e1767b187","tid":1527881,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:48:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b71bc64b2a3246eb3f9a7dec2bdc7b674d2d70a","tid":1527881,"uid":194069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:49:09.000Z","msg":"9293 三罷"},{"pid":"eb6de9c9c07d351773f1f4598093b0002de7e800","tid":1527881,"uid":194069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:49:19.000Z","msg":"9293 三罷"},{"pid":"ed6a4a3f73e5d58a0a9188c517a5f6ff103e992f","tid":1527881,"uid":194069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:49:37.000Z","msg":"9293 三罷"},{"pid":"3b4f18bcb6d0110d0832be8fd38a34777f3c18ea","tid":1527881,"uid":194069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:49:48.000Z","msg":"9293 三罷"},{"pid":"364f2a451a28286e89bf2773ce2aca7396ce86b2","tid":1527881,"uid":212182,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:49:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XejD7PR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXejD7PR.jpg&h=19bacab6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b8d90230914e8ce17f3d060d1a2a1c0c3bf7bdf","tid":1527881,"uid":40628,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:50:02.000Z","msg":"成條機鐵東涌線停咗，台灣班機都證實政治唔俾機進入，算係咁，走遲半步真係會成班被圍捕"},{"pid":"759e50398982e9412970e17e081f64c01a767c10","tid":1527881,"uid":194069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:50:07.000Z","msg":"9293 三罷"},{"pid":"bb7b9978dae7cc8b751abee57a87d7833b022a06","tid":1527881,"uid":22054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201